function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	if Drop_PRD:Roll() then
		if not Hydra.ActorHasItemByName(idSelf, tRelics[1]) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSelf) then
			Hydra.ItemDropAtActor(idSelf, tRelics[1], true, idActor);
		end
	end

end
